places.access:
■電車：JR京浜東北線 北浦和駅西口下車、徒歩約8分です。
 西口を出たら左側を歩き、前方の北浦和公園表口から入り、近代美術館を通り過ぎた裏口から公園を出ます。
 出てすぐ左に曲がり、小学校を超えて最初の十字路(酒屋と花屋の間)を右に曲がると左側に見えてきます。
 ■車：①中山道から→[北浦和駅前]交差点 から浦所線(埼大通り)に入り、２つ目の信号(左に森熊美術館がある交差点)を左折。直進約400mの左側です。②大宮バイパスから→ロジャースの角を浦和所沢線(埼大通り)に入り、サティを通り過ぎ、右に森熊美術館のある交差点を右折。直進約400mの左側です。
 ■電車：ＪＲ京浜東北線 北浦和駅西口下車、徒歩8分。
 ＪＲ埼京線 南与野駅下車、徒歩15分(タクシーで5分程)
places.accessEn:
Train: Take the JR Keihin Tohoku Line, get off at Kita-Urawa Station West Exit, and walk about 8 minutes.
 After exiting the West Exit, walk on the left side of the street, enter from the front exit of Kita-Urawa Park in front of you, and exit the park from the back exit past the Museum of Modern Art.
 Turn left immediately after exiting the park, go past the elementary school and turn right at the first crossroad (between a liquor store and a flower shop), and you will see it on the left.
Take JR Saikyo Line and get off at Minami-Yono Station. 15 minutes on foot (about 5 minutes by taxi).
 By car: (1) From Nakasendo→Take the Uradokoro Line (Saitama Univ. Dori) from the [Kita-Urawa Ekimae] intersection, and turn left at the second traffic light (intersection with the Morikuma Museum on the left). Go straight for about 400m and it is on the left. (2) From Omiya Bypass→Turn onto the Urawa-Tokorozawa line (Saikyo Boulevard) at the corner of Rogers, pass by Saty, and turn right at the intersection with the Mori Bear Museum on the right. Go straight for about 400m and it is on the left.
